The ClassRigh typo below results in an internal error:

```
class ClsRight;
   string m_s;
endclass

module t (/*AUTOARG*/);
   string s;
   initial begin
      // verilator lint_off PKGNODECL
      s = ClsRigh::m_s;  // Bad typo
   end
endmodule

```

See test_regress/t/t_class_ref_bad.v
